description: This class holds constants for special keys See: https://w3c.github.io/uievents-key/#keys-special See: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyboardEvent/key/Key_Values#Special_values

members.description: The user agent wasn't able to map the event's virtual keycode to a specific key value. This can happen due to hardware or software constraints, or because of constraints around the platform on which the user agent is running.
